Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.72,0:00:02.31,TOA08,,0000,0000,0000,,Kto si?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.06,0:00:04.30,TOA08,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáč.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.48,0:00:07.77,TOA08,,0000,0000,0000,,Asi som na teba pravdepodobne zabudla.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.35,0:00:09.28,TOA08,,0000,0000,0000,,To som ja!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.36,0:00:10.72,TOA08,,0000,0000,0000,,Som, Niiya Teiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.95,0:00:13.79,TOA08,,0000,0000,0000,,Aha, voláš sa Teiichi-kun, že?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.14,0:00:16.54,TOA08,,0000,0000,0000,,Rada ťa spoznávam, Teiichi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.70,0:00:20.56,TOA08,,0000,0000,0000,,A, zbohom, Teiichi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.64,0:00:23.85,TOA08,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(216,464)}Už nechodievaj za mnou.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.64,0:00:23.65,nech,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(474,420)}Už nechodievaj za mnou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.18,0:00:27.12,TOA08,,0000,0000,0000,,Určite si niekto, kto mi spôsobil utrpenie.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.35,0:00:29.66,TOA08h,,0000,0000,0000,,Preto som na teba zabudla.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.97,0:00:32.09,TOA08h,,0000,0000,0000,,Kvôli tomu by sme sa už nemali stretávať.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.18,0:00:34.77,TOA08h,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja som ti spôsobil utrpenie, Yuuko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.50,0:00:37.70,TOA08,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo máš nohu v sádre?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.72,0:00:41.03,TOA08,,0000,0000,0000,,Je možné, že je to kvôli mne?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.88,0:00:43.92,TOA08,,0000,0000,0000,,Tušila som to. Nesmieme sa stretávať.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.48,0:00:46.00,TOA08,,0000,0000,0000,,Aj pre tvoje dobro.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.38,0:00:47.88,TOA08,,0000,0000,0000,,To nie, Yuuko-san...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.97,0:00:49.79,TOA08,,0000,0000,0000,,Prestaň, nedotýkaj sa ma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.01,0:00:54.33,TOA08,,0000,0000,0000,,Kto si?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.02,0:00:58.09,TOA08,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuukine spomienky zmizli?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.20,0:01:01.80,TOA08,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, aj spomienky, ktoré sa týkali mňa...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.80,0:01:04.27,TOA08,,0000,0000,0000,,... boli úplne odstránené.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.68,0:01:08.79,TOA08,,0000,0000,0000,,Taktiež, sa už až tak neteší z mojej prítomnosti, ako stále...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.02,0:01:11.20,TOA08,,0000,0000,0000,,... akoby bola nejako osamelá.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.02,0:01:13.01,TOA08,,0000,0000,0000,,Aha.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.23,0:01:17.12,TOA08,,0000,0000,0000,,Tušila som, že Yuuko si môže pravdepodobne odvrhnúť svoje spomienky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.84,0:01:20.21,TOA08,,0000,0000,0000,,Odvrhnúť svoje spomienky?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.56,0:01:26.31,TOA08,,0000,0000,0000,,Aby mohla ochrániť samú seba, pravdepodobne odvrhla všetky svoje negatívne, alebo nepríjemné spomienky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.75,0:01:29.70,TOA08,,0000,0000,0000,,Niiya, pobil si sa pred Yuukou s niekým?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.72,0:01:30.53,TOA08,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.97,0:01:34.38,TOA08,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale, kvôli čomu ťa Yuuko strčila zo schodov?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.94,0:01:42.04,TOA08,,0000,0000,0000,,Mýliš sa...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:43.57,TOA08,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-san, by toto...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.72,0:01:45.80,TOA08,,0000,0000,0000,,Určite to bola iba nejaká náhoda.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.92,0:01:47.74,TOA08,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak keď to bola iba náhoda...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.90,0:01:51.22,TOA08,,0000,0000,0000,,... terajšia Yuuko, sa snaží držať si od teba odstup.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.47,0:01:53.49,TOA08,,0000,0000,0000,,Či je to kvôli pocitu viny...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.61,0:01:56.15,TOA08,,0000,0000,0000,,... alebo má na to iný dôvod, tak to neviem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.75,0:02:01.97,TOA08,,0000,0000,0000,,Avšak, odvrhla si svoje spomienky na teba, Niiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.06,0:02:03.35,TOA08,,0000,0000,0000,,Zabudnutie...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.41,0:02:05.18,TOA08,,0000,0000,0000,,... strata určitých spomienok...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.57,0:02:08.01,TOA08,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to AMNÉZIA.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.81,0:02:15.31,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Rozpáľ ma
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.81,0:02:15.31,OPka,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}watashi yo moete
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.31,0:02:23.90,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Rozpáľ ma v objatí. Nie je hriechom pokúsiť sa ma objať, že?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.31,0:02:23.90,OPka,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}moete dakishimete miru no wa tsumi jyanai desshou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.90,0:02:25.78,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Prečistiť temnotu ohňom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.90,0:02:25.78,OPka,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}himei yami wo harae
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.78,0:02:30.66,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,2033)}Zbor spútaných
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.78,0:02:30.66,OPka,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,2033)}Choir jail
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.87,0:02:36.25,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Smútiaci nedonútia vás splniť si sny
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.87,0:02:36.25,OPka,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}nageite mo yume wa utawanai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.50,0:02:42.21,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Vykríkla som, "Kto mi dá odpoveď"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.50,0:02:42.21,OPka,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}koko de sakendayo kotae wa dare ga motteru no
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.63,0:02:46.97,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Nevšimneš si to, ak budeš mať zvesenú hlavu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.63,0:02:46.97,OPka,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}utsumuita mama jya kizukanai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.97,0:02:53.18,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Budem hľadať budúcnosť v tvojich očiach
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.97,0:02:53.18,OPka,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}kimi no hitomi no naka mirai wo sagasu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.51,0:02:58.19,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Ak sa teraz stane nejaký zázrak
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.51,0:02:58.19,OPka,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}moshimo kiseki ga ima mo sasu nara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.19,0:03:00.86,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Utri si uplakané oči
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.19,0:03:00.86,OPka,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}nijimu namida meguute
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.86,0:03:03.52,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}a poďme vpred.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.86,0:03:03.52,OPka,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}mae muite arukou
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.82,0:03:08.24,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Otvor sa mi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.82,0:03:08.24,OPka,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}watashi wo akete
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.49,0:03:14.29,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Okrem tohto utrpenia nevidím nič iné
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.49,0:03:14.29,OPka,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}konna kurushisa de nanimo mienai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:19.29,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Rozpálim sa
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:19.29,OPka,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}watashi yo moete
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.29,0:03:27.05,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Byť vášnivým nie je hriechom, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.29,0:03:27.05,OPka,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}moete kanata he jyounetsu wa tsumi jyanai deshou
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:29.51,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Prečistiť temnotu
