Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.16,0:23:40.24,TOA08,,0000,0000,0000,,Spomienky sa stratili.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.79,0:23:43.37,TOA08,,0000,0000,0000,,Znovu a ešte raz.
